## Third-Party Acknowledgments

WX (Weather Alerts) is an independent, open-source MeshMonitor Auto Responder script designed to integrate with:

- MeshMonitor (by Yeraze)
- Meshtastic (open-source LoRa mesh networking platform)
- The National Weather Service (NWS) public API at https://api.weather.gov/

This project uses publicly available NWS alert data but does not rebroadcast NOAA Weather Radio audio and is not affiliated with NOAA or the National Weather Service.

All trademarks, logos, and brand names are the property of their respective owners.  
WX (Weather Alerts) is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or officially connected to MeshMonitor, Meshtastic, NOAA, the National Weather Service, or any other referenced platform or provider.
